{"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"platforms":["iOS"],"tokens":[{"text":"+ (","kind":"text"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"void","preciseIdentifier":"c:v"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"text":"handlePushRegistration:","kind":"identifier"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)NSData","text":"NSData"},{"kind":"text","text":" *) "},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"deviceToken"},{"kind":"text","text":";"}],"languages":["occ"]}]},{"kind":"parameters","parameters":[{"name":"deviceToken","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The device token Data received from APNs","type":"text"}]}]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"anchor":"discussion","text":"Discussion","type":"heading","level":2},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Call this method from your AppDelegate’s "},{"code":"application:didRegisterForRemoteNotificationsWithDeviceToken:","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"to forward the device token to Pushwoosh."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The SDK normally handles this automatically via method swizzling, but you may need to call"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"this directly if:","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"You’ve disabled swizzling","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"You’re managing multiple push providers"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"You need custom token processing","type":"text"}]}]}]},{"anchor":"Example","type":"heading","text":"Example","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Manual token handling with multiple push providers:"}]},{"type":"codeListing","code":["class AppDelegate: UIResponder, UIApplicationDelegate {","","    func application(_ application: UIApplication,","                    didRegisterForRemoteNotificationsWithDeviceToken deviceToken: Data) {","","        \/\/ Convert token to string for logging","        let tokenString = deviceToken.map { String(format: \"%02.2hhx\", $0) }.joined()","        Logger.info(\"Received APNs token: \\(tokenString.prefix(20))...\")","","        \/\/ Send to Pushwoosh","        Pushwoosh.configure.handlePushRegistration(deviceToken)","","        \/\/ Send to other push providers if needed","        FirebaseMessaging.messaging().apnsToken = deviceToken","","        \/\/ Sync with backend","        BackendAPI.shared.updatePushToken(tokenString)","    }","}"],"syntax":"swift"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Only use this method if you need manual control."}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"sections":[],"kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Manually handles the device push token registration."}],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"occ","url":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration\/handlePushRegistration:"},"metadata":{"fragments":[{"kind":"text","text":"+ "},{"text":"handlePushRegistration:","kind":"identifier"}],"symbolKind":"method","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"handlePushRegistration:","kind":"identifier"}],"title":"handlePushRegistration:","role":"symbol","modules":[{"name":"PushwooshCore"}],"roleHeading":"Type Method","externalID":"c:objc(pl)PWConfiguration(cm)handlePushRegistration:"},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore","doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration"]]},"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"patch":0,"major":0},"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration\/handlepushregistration:"]}],"references":{"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore/PWConfiguration/handlePushRegistration:":{"url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration\/handlepushregistra